SdioCommonInfo¶

Overview¶

Related Modules:

SDIO

Description:

Defines SDIO common information.

You can obtain and set common SDIO information by calling SdioGetCommonInfo and SdioSetCommonInfo with SdioCommonInfo and SdioCommonInfoType passed.
